<font color="#11FF11">Why on Earth would Drusus want</font>
<font color="#11FF11">to murder his best friend</font>

20:01.618 --> 20:03.617
<font color="#11FF11">and business partner?</font>

20:03.618 --> 20:05.977
<font color="#00FFFF">Well, clearly having his way</font>
<font color="#00FFFF">with my wife was not enough,</font>

20:05.978 --> 20:09.457
<font color="#00FFFF">he wanted to get his hands</font>
<font color="#00FFFF">on my company, too!</font>

20:09.458 --> 20:12.457
<font color="#11FF11">What are you talking about, husband?</font>
<font color="#FFFF00">Oh, come on,</font>

20:12.458 --> 20:15.617
<font color="#FFFF00">Clodia, we've known about your</font>
<font color="#FFFF00">tawdry little affair for years!</font>

20:15.618 --> 20:18.617
<font color="#00FFFF">Yes, all those visits</font>
<font color="#00FFFF">to your so-called pustulous aunt.</font>

20:18.618 --> 20:21.977
<font color="#11FF11">She is pustulous,</font>
<font color="#11FF11">I was draining her weeping sores.</font>

20:21.978 --> 20:25.617
<font color="#00FFFF">You were plotting my death with your</font>
<font color="#00FFFF">lover, don't you dare deny it!</font>

20:25.618 --> 20:26.618
<font color="#11FF11">Well, do you blame me?</font>

20:26.619 --> 20:28.617
<font color="#11FF11">With a husband</font>
<font color="#11FF11">who won't even look at me</font>

20:28.618 --> 20:31.617
<font color="#11FF11">because he's too busy</font>
<font color="#11FF11">fucking Petronius!</font>

20:31.618 --> 20:33.298
OTHERS GASP

20:36.618 --> 20:39.617
Thank you so much
for a lovely evening,

20:39.618 --> 20:41.977
perhaps we could have you round
to ours some time?

20:41.978 --> 20:43.617
<font color="#FFFF00">No, never, leave at once.</font>

20:43.618 --> 20:47.617
Sure, just... I wonder whether,
seeing as we solved the murder,

20:47.618 --> 20:50.617
and in a way saved your life,
would you maybe reconsider

20:50.618 --> 20:52.617
helping with the late licence
application?

20:52.618 --> 20:57.617
<font color="#FFFF00">Shoo, now, before I summon Herbo.</font>
Yes, no, will do, goodbye.

20:57.618 --> 21:01.977
<font color="#00FFFF">Rufina, hey, I was gonna say,</font>
<font color="#00FFFF">now you're officially a widow,</font>

21:01.978 --> 21:05.617
<font color="#00FFFF">maybe we should hook up sometime</font>
<font color="#00FFFF">for another cheeky poetry recital?</font>

21:05.618 --> 21:09.617
<font color="#FFFF00">Oh, you're very sweet,</font>
<font color="#FFFF00">like a licky little dog,</font>

21:09.618 --> 21:13.617
<font color="#FFFF00">but now I'm a widow, I've come into</font>
<font color="#FFFF00">a very large sum of money.</font>

21:13.618 --> 21:14.618
<font color="#00FFFF">Oh, wicked, well done.</font>

21:14.619 --> 21:18.617
<font color="#FFFF00">So if I want a handsome stud to read</font>
<font color="#FFFF00">me Greek poetry, then, well,</font>

21:18.618 --> 21:21.618
<font color="#FFFF00">I'll probably just go to Greece.</font>

21:25.658 --> 21:28.297
<font color="#FFFF00">Call that a banquet?</font>
<font color="#FFFF00">I only had a few nibbles.</font>

21:28.298 --> 21:30.137
<font color="#00FFFF">Tell me about it, I'm starving.</font>

21:30.138 --> 21:32.617
We could always get that kebab.
<font color="#00FFFF">Now you're talking!</font>

21:32.618 --> 21:35.617
The Longinus Brothers can keep
their bullshit banquets.

21:35.618 --> 21:38.617
<font color="#00FFFF">Keep them! </font>Argh! Not my back,
that's where I got whipped.

